Had some cancelations with the suites. The Lord and Lady who had been using the Minister's Suite pulled out after they found out half the casino was shut down tonight. They left in a huff, and didn't even bother to get their stuff out of the suite. Someone needs to go secure their valuables before the guards do it. Also, our honored guest Lady Antonette has mysteriously elected to not stay the night. Seems to me she doesn't plan on winning this haggle, but you didn't hear that from me. Remember to check her suite too. These folk always forget something. - G"